[This media report arrived several hours before the weekly summary and most likely refers to one of the 3 newly confirmed cases mentioned in section [1] above.

A map of Afghanistan showing provinces can be found at http://ontheworldmap.com/afghanistan/administrative-map-of-afghanistan-with-provinces-and-districts.jpg. Note that Chora district is in the center of the country, bordering with Gizab district in Daykundi province. - Mod.MPP]

